This app brings classic chess game into new dimension. With advanced 3D graphics you can feel all beauty of interacting with virtual chess set. Choose to play with AI or with real opponents. 

Game Features:

* Advanced 3D graphics;
* Online gameplay. More than 1 million registered users worldwide.
* Matchmaking feature;
* Chat with opponents while playing online;
* AI with 2400 levels of difficulty;
* Hints for beginners - highlighting of possible moves;
* Different themes of chess set;
* 3D and 2D board variants; 
* Both landscape and portrait screen mode supported.

Chess is one of the best and interesting games on Earth! It is played by millions players around the world, from children to the elderly. But to understand how to play chess, it is not enough just know chess rules and names of chess pieces. It is much more important to learn chess strategy and tactics, as well as all the fields of the chess board to navigate it well.

Our app contains more than 2500 chess puzzles and several chess openings. And all of this is absolutely free! Each puzzle reveals to some tactic or trick. You have to guess the next chess move to solve the puzzle and move on to the next one.

Chess puzzle games are very effective in progress and learning. And if you train every day with our app, your chess game will improve quickly, because your combination vision can easily find the trick in a real game with an opponent.

Download the app "Chess Coach" and you will get:
• 2500 chess puzzles;
• Daily bonus in the game;
• 12 thematic sections;
• Three difficulty levels: easy, medium and difficult;
• Tips in each puzzle.

Play chess with our app "Chess Coach"!

